files.name: .editorconfig
files.content:
# http://editorconfig.org
root = true

[*]
indent_style = space
indent_size = 2
charset = utf-8
trim_trailing_whitespace = true
insert_final_newline = true
end_of_line = lf

[*.md]
trim_trailing_whitespace = false

files.name: .travis.yml
files.content:
language: node_js
node_js:
  - 8
  - 10
  - 12
  - 14
  - lts/*
# Send coverage data to Coveralls
after_script: "cat ./coverage/lcov.info | ./node_modules/coveralls/bin/coveralls.js"

tsconfig.json
files.content:
{
  "compilerOptions": {
    "declaration": true,
    "module": "commonjs",
    "lib": ["es6"],
    "newLine": "LF",
    "noEmitHelpers": true,
    "noImplicitAny": false,
    "noImplicitThis": true,
    "noUnusedLocals": true,
    "noUnusedParameters": true,
    "strictNullChecks": true,
    "strictFunctionTypes": true,
    "target": "es5",

    "baseUrl": ".",
    "paths": { "immutability-helper": ["."] }
  },
  "files": [
    "index.ts"
  ]
}
